	<h2>Timelines, Maps and Charts</h2>
	<p><a href="http://timeline.knightlab.com/">TimelineJS</a><br />Interactive timelines that support media embeds from Twitter, Flickr, Google Maps, YouTube, Vimeo, Vine, Dailymotion, Wikipedia, SoundCloud and more.</p>
